I"î<p>A few simple configs to change after an initial install</p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">_config.yml</code></p>

<p><strong>description</strong></p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">description: &gt; # this means to ignore newlines until "baseurl:"</code></p>

<p><code class="highlighter-rouge">Change your description here.
 You can make it multi-line as described in the comment above.</code></p>

<p><strong>permalinks</strong>
<code class="highlighter-rouge">permalink: /blog/:year/:title</code></p>

<p><strong>pagination</strong></p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>  paginate: 5
  paginate_path: <span class="s2">"blog/page:num/"</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
